article.headline: St. Louis 63, Troy 55
article.story: CHARLOTTE AMALIE, U.S. Virgin Islands (AP) -- Reggie Bryant led St. Louis past Troy State on Monday, taking fifth place in the Paradise Jam tournament. Bryant had 15 points, six rebounds and six assists for the Billikens. Eddie Baker led Troy State with 19.
